<text name="text_PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT_1">Sensors go wild as a nearby pulsar is detected. While you are attempting to recalibrate the FTL drive, a pirate sneaks up on your ship, weapons charging. Prepare for a fight! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="text_PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT_2">You arrive to find a pulsar dominating the view screen. You see a small silhouette pass in front of the star. Before you can ponder what it is, warning signals go off. It appears to be a ship in a firing trajectory! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="text_PIRATE_PULSAR_TEXT_3">A small research station orbits a nearby pulsar. It appears largely abandoned, but you detect power signatures flaring up as soon as you're in scanning distance. A small combat ship launches from the station. Pirates! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="text_REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT_1">A Rebel captain appears on the screen. "I thought we had been doomed to backwater assignments. This is my chance to get back in Command's good graces! Charge the weapons!" [ Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 2-3, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="text_REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT_2">A small rebel research station overlooks a pulsating star. Before you can react a Rebel ship spots you and moves in to attack. [ Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 2-3, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="text_REBEL_PULSAR_TEXT_3">You arrive at an infrequently used beacon close to a pulsar. Before long a Rebel ship happens to jump nearby. Looks like you'll have to fight. [ Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards w/Pulsar; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 2-3, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>

