<text name="event_MANTIS_CIVILIAN_c2_choice">Stay out of it. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_CREW_c1_choice">Jettison the pod. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_CREW_c2_choice">Pry it open. [ Crew Loss (Clone Bay Revive), 1 Mantis Boarder | Mantis Crew Gain | HumanCrew Gain ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_FIGHT_CHOICE_c1_choice">Attack the ship. [ Mantis Ship Fight Default Rewards ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_FIGHT_CHOICE_c2_choice">Attempt to remain concealed. [ Nothing Happens | x2 Mantis Ship Fight Default Rewards ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_FIGHT_CHOICE_c3_choice">(Cloaking) Cloak to stay hidden. [ x2 Nothing Happens | Mantis Ship Fight Default Rewards ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_NAMED_THIEF_DEFEAT_c1_choice">Move in to strip their ship. [ High Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_NAMED_THIEF_DEFEAT_c2_c1_choice">Put him out of his misery. [ High Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_MANTIS_NAMED_THIEF_DEFEAT_c2_c2_choice">Listen to what he has to say. [ High Standard, High Scrap & Weapon Quest ]</text>
