<text name="event_CONTACT_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c3_choice">(Slug) "Sir: We can dock, but I sense that we better plan on making a purchase..." [ Missle Offers or -3 Hull and Ship Fight Default Rewards if none are purchased ]</text>
