<text name="event_DOCK_DRONE_SALESMAN_c6_text">"Ah, I'Med. sorry to hear that! Pleasant journeys." Once back to the helm, a series of explosions rocks your ship. The pirate ship has powered its weapons! You receive a message, "You shouldn't waste people's time Captain!" [ -3 Hull, Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_c1_choice">Move in to examine the station. [ Nothing Happens | x2 LScrap | [ LSCrap | Clone Bay Blue Option [ x2 Crew Gain | 1 Boarder ] ] | 2 Boarders, Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards | 2-4 Boarders, Enemy ASB ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_c2_choice">Stay near the Beacon. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_4_c1_choice">(Clone Bay) Search for a surviving DNA bank. [ x2 Crew Gain | 1 Boarder ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_4_c2_choice">Scrap the machinery. [ LScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_5_text">You dock with the station to take a look inside. However no sooner do you open the airlock than pirates burst in. Meanwhile scanners pick up a previously undetected pirate ship moving in to attack! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards; 2 Boarders; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_EMPTY_STATION2_LIST_6_text">You dock with the station to take a look inside. However no sooner do you open the airlock than pirates burst in. Meanwhile multiple warning signals go off on the bridge. The pirates have activated a remote planetary defense system and it's locking onto your ship! [ 2-4 Boarders, EnemyASB ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_c1_choice">Dock with the refueling platform. [ [ Fuel Trade | 3-5 Fuel | More... ] | [ [ -3 Hull, 2-4 Boarders | 5 Fuel Bla Standardoors Blue Option ] | -3 Hull, Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards ] ]</text>
