<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_PIRATE_LIST_2_text">The refueling station welcomes you into one of its berths, and as you hail them, there is an explosion from your engine room! While assessing the damage, you detect a Pirate Ship closing fast! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards, -3 Hull; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_2_c1_choice">Steal it. [ +3-5 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_FUELING_STATION_NORMAL_LIST_2_c2_choice">War doesn't justify abandoning one's values. You leave it alone. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
