<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_c3_choice">Decline. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_HELP_MINERS_c1_choice">(Missile Weapon) Offer to solve their problem by launching a missile. [ Same as above ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_2_text">A complete scan of the planet reveals no life signs other than a single ship on the surface. The terraformers thank you for your help, and attempt to contact the ship. Just as you're about to jump away, the ship takes off and attacks, it's a pirate! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, RStuf; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_choice">Tell them to stop. Any life is valuable. [ 15-25 Scrap or -15-25 Scrap for Oxygen +1 or Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_c1_choice">Accept the bribe and leave. [ 15-25 Scrap ]</text>
