<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c1_c3_choice">Power your weapons and demand they leave at once. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_HIGH_SCAN_TERRAFORMING_3_c2_choice">Leave them to their work.</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c1_choice">Hail the ship. [ More ... ]</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c2_choice">Attack him before he can attack! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_PIRATE_SALESMAN_c3_choice">Quickly prepare to jump away. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
