<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_choice">(Lanius Crew) Offer to have your crewmember help. [ MScrap or High Scrap & Augment for Lanius trade ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_c1_c1_choice">Ask your crew if they agree. [ High Scrap & Augment, Lanius Crew Loss ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_c3_c1_c2_choice">Our crew is not for sale. [ MScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_1_c1_choice">Attack the Rebels to help them escape. [ Rebel Ship Fight Enemy ASB; Kill Reward: Med. Standard; Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: MScrap ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_1_c2_choice">Leave. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_2_c1_choice">Move in to examine the station. [ Nothing Happens | x2 LScrap | [ LScrap | Clone Bay Blue Option [ x2 Crew Gain | 1 Boarder ] ] | 2 Boarders, Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards | 2-4 Boarders, Enemy ASB ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_2_c2_choice">Stay near the Beacon. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c1_choice">Give them the requested 4 fuel. [ MScrap, -4 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c2_choice">Give them 1 fuel. [ -1 Fuel ]</text>
<text name="event_QUEST_CONSTRUCTIONYARD_LIST_3_c3_choice">Do not give them any. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_BRIBE_RESULT_4_text">One of the civilian ships contacts you and reveals they are Federation loyalists. An eavesdropping Rebel swoops in, destroys the ship, and turns to attack you! [ Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 2-3, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_CHECKPOINT_c1_choice">Fend for yourself, attack and escape. [ Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 2-3, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 3-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_CHECKPOINT_c2_choice">Bribe the Rebels to release the civilian ships. [ Nothing Happens | LScrap | Low Standard | Rebel Ship Fight Default Rewards ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c1_choice">Attack the Rebels. [ Rebel Ship Fight Kill Reward: Low Standard, Crew Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Double Reward: Nothing Happens or [ Low Scrap & Drones | Nothing Happens | LScrap | -2 Hull ] ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c2_choice">Wait and steal the supplies from the civilians. [ Low Scrap & Drones | Nothing Happens | LScrap | -2 Hull ]</text>
<text name="event_REBEL_HELPERS_c3_choice">Leave them be. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
