<text name="event_REFUGEE_GHOST_c2_choice">Ignore the ship. [ Nothing Happens ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_1_text">As you hail the freighter, it advances, weapons bristling from its hull! It's a pirate ambush! [ Pirate Ship Fight Default Rewards; Surrender (Chance, Min-Max, Offer): 0.5, 3-4, Random Resources; Escape (Chance, Min-Max, Timer): 0.5, 2-4 ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_2_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a Zoltan ship suddenly jumps into the system... it claims the refugees are criminals, and accuses you of escorting fugitives! Before you can respond, it cuts communications, and powers up its weapons! [ Zoltan Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_3_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a pirate ship jumps into the system... it was using the refugee ship as bait! [ Pirate Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_4_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a Slug ship jumps into the system... it was hunting the refugee ship for sport and now they've found you instead! [ Slug Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_PIRATE_1_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a pirate ship jumps into the system... it was using the refugee ship as bait! [ Pirate Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_SLUG_1_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a pirate ship jumps into the system... it was using the refugee ship as bait! [ Pirate Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
<text name="event_REFUGEE_HAIL_LIST_ZOLTAN_1_text">As you hail the refugee ship, a Zoltan ship suddenly jumps into the system... it claims the refugees are criminals, and accuses you of escorting fugitives! Before you can respond, it cuts communications, and powers up its weapons! [ Zoltan Ship Fight Kill Reward: Med. Standard, Crew Kill Reward: High Standard, Double Reward: Low Standard ]</text>
